The data model I would use

Use a list of dictionaries.

Example:

[
    {"crossing": "Zosin", "vehicle": "car", "wait_hours": 2},
    {"crossing": "Dorohusk", "vehicle": "car", "wait_hours": 5}
]

Why this works:
	•	easy to print
	•	easy to sort
	•	easy to save
	•	easy to expand later

